## рҹҸ—пёҸ Design Outline

### Goals
| Concern | Decision |
|---|---|
| Queue type | **Bounded** (buffered channel) вҖ” applies backpressure to callers |
| Results | **Callback per job** вҖ” avoids a separate result-collection goroutine |
| Shutdown flavour | **Two-tier**: `Shutdown()` (graceful, drains queue) + `ForceShutdown()` (immediate, drops pending) |
| Submit-after-shutdown | **Safe** вҖ” guarded by `sync.Once` + atomic state, never panics |
| Goroutine leaks | **None** вҖ” `sync.WaitGroup` ensures every worker is joined |

---

### Core Components

